HEADWORD: desexualize
<hw>desexualize</hw> <pos>v. i. & t.</pos> <def>to direct one's
libidinous urges into another direction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>same as <er>desex</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> sterilize, desex, unsex, fix, make
infertile.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

